**To-Do App Overview**
======================
The to-do app will allow users to create, read, update, and delete (CRUD) tasks. The app will utilize local storage to store tasks, ensuring that data persists even after the user closes the browser.

**App Features**
---------------

*   **Task Creation**: Users can create new tasks with a title and description.
*   **Task Display**: The app will display all tasks in a list, including their title, description, and completion status.
*   **Task Update**: Users can update the title, description, and completion status of existing tasks.
*   **Task Deletion**: Users can delete tasks from the list.
*   **Local Storage**: Tasks will be stored in the browser's local storage, allowing data to persist between sessions.

